					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10361450#post-4262889</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10361450/scp-4138#post-4262889</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2019 03:33:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>WarpZone</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>147364</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>For some reason, I thought I was just reading phase one of the document, and it was going to ask me for 0-5 clearence so it could tell me what was <em>really</em> going on. Then dat quote.</p> <p>It was a sudden ending, and an abrupt ending, and maybe a bit too upbeat for a creepypasta.</p> <p>But it at least <strong>was</strong> an ending. And after running across one too many shaggy dog stories today, I respect that.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
